disgusting sound effects every time you slam a furniture scavenging house for supplies;
it's not clear why only husband tries to take everything useful to the shelter: other family members continue to do their personal stuff despite the alarming signal - why he should take these idiots to the shelter if they aren't smart enough to evacuate themselves?
Such game demands a constant updates bringing new items

